Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:46.09,Title_eps,,0,0,0,,{\fad(274,0)\q2\blur0.8\fscy70\fscx333\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\pos(325,365)}Kurata 6-dan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:03.23,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:07.04,Background,,0,0,0,,They're not all playing games either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.37,0:02:09.23,Background,,0,0,0,,There are tutoring games and lectures, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But... wow, there are a lot of people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:17.33,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, Hikaru! Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:18.24,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs17\1c&H000000&\blur0.8\bord0\fscy80\frz359\shad0\pos(75,106)}{\alpha&HFF&}Net {\alpha&H00&}Go Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:20.75,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs17\1c&H000000&\blur0.8\bord0\shad0\fscy80\frz359\pos(75,106)}Net Go Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:26.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I guess this'll cheer Sai up a bit. I'm glad we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:31.55,Memory,,0,0,0,,I wanted to play you with no handicap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:41.01,Memory,,0,0,0,,Next time, let us play an even game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.43,Memory,,0,0,0,,Yes, let us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:48.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It did turn out to be an unsatisfying game for Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.97,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:54.45,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, let's go watch a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And let's go watch Ochi's\Nnew first dan match next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That jerk was dissing my game\Nwith Waya. I've got to get him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:11.63,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru's trying to be nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:18.92,Sai,,0,0,0,,When I took an important game\Naway from him by being selfish...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:21.96,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'm the one that's at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:24.48,Sai,,0,0,0,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:27.10,Sai,,0,0,0,,I won't ask him to play someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:29.26,Sai,,0,0,0,,too often.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.82,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz345\pos(422,241)}Vendor's Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.46,0:03:34.20,Background,,0,0,0,,That'll be 1,500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:41.82,Background,,0,0,0,,You've got to stop selling those cheap\Nfans, and start selling the expensive Go boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Gokiso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,THAT treasure of a board hasn't sold yet,\Nbut I've already sold three of the other ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Which ones have you sold?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:55.42,Background,,0,0,0,,This one! The Kaya Go board! Special, 200,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:04:02.33,Background,,0,0,0,,This is Kaya? Well I guess you can fool most\Npeople with it. But it's probably only worth 80,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hand the pen over. You\Ncan't just put 'special' on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:13.98,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz6\pos(261,22)}Kaya Go Board
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:13.98,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H2407CE&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fs17.5\frz6\pos(171,45)}S\NP\NE\NC\NI\NA\NL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:14.03,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz6\pos(271,47)}Kaya Go Board
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:14.03,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H2407CE&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fs17.5\frz6\pos(182,70)}S\NP\NE\NC\NI\NA\NL
