Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:14.15,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H2407CE&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fs17.5\frz6\pos(195,99)}S\NP\NE\NC\NI\NA\NL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:14.19,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz6\pos(294,102)}Kaya Go Board
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.15,0:04:14.19,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H2407CE&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fs17.5\frz6\pos(206,125)}S\NP\NE\NC\NI\NA\NL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:14.32,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz6\pos(304,125)}Kaya Go Board
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:14.32,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H2407CE&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fs17.5\frz6\pos(217,149)}S\NP\NE\NC\NI\NA\NL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:14.36,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz6\pos(312,143)}Kaya Go Board
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:14.36,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H2407CE&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fs17.5\frz6\pos(224,167)}S\NP\NE\NC\NI\NA\NL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:17.11,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz6\pos(316,152)}Kaya Go Board
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:17.11,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H2407CE&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fs17.5\frz6\pos(228,175)}S\NP\NE\NC\NI\NA\NL
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:17.11,Background,,0,0,0,,This is much more useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem like you're better at business than Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding, I'm a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, I'm the reason\Nyou got into this convention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Work hard at getting their money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:35.42,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs25\1c&H000000&\fscy140\bord0\shad0\frz348\pos(333,166)}FREE PLAY AREA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:34.75,Sai,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.06,0:04:38.63,Sai,,0,0,0,,That large cluster is about to get taken. It's in atari.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:44.08,Thinking,,0,0,0,,You're right. This is no time to\Nbe thinking, he's got to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.09,Sai,,0,0,0,,He didn't notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll get taken this turn, and the game'll end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:57.44,Sai,,0,0,0,,AHH! He hasn't noticed either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:05:01.77,Sai,,0,0,0,,T-This is much more exciting than a pro match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:06.30,Background,,0,0,0,,Would you like to play?\NWe're still registering players.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Play? No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:12.01,Sai,,0,0,0,,I'll play if you don't want to, Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:18.02,Sai,,0,0,0,,I just told myself not to ask. I'm so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:21.34,Background,,0,0,0,,A Go board, they're so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.51,Background,,0,0,0,,I'd like to buy one some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not buy it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'd improve\Nquicker if you played on a good board.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're just selling boards and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:36.70,Sai,,0,0,0,,What were you expecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:40.05,Background,,0,0,0,,There's a special on this one today, just 25,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:46.16,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz6\pos(316,152)}Kaya Go Board
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:46.16,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H2407CE&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fs17.5\frz6\pos(228,175)}S\NP\NE\NC\NI\NA\NL
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:42.90,Background,,0,0,0,,That one's on special for just 200,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:46.16,Background,,0,0,0,,It's made out of the best\Ndomestic grown Kaya there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.51,Sai,,0,0,0,,Kaya!? This is Kaya!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:53.17,Sai,,0,0,0,,This isn't Kaya. It looks like it, but it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.58,0:05:55.09,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai, what's Kaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:57.44,Sai,,0,0,0,,It's a wood used to make Go boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.94,Sai,,0,0,0,,Your grandfather's board is made of Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:02.17,Sai,,0,0,0,,All good boards are made of Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:03.58,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What about mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:05.06,Sai,,0,0,0,,That's Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:05.85,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't Kaya!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop making up stuff to ruin my business!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:15.19,Background,,0,0,0,,Who's causing the trouble over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in the way of his business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:23.23,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, try placing a stone on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,AHH! What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.63,Sai,,0,0,0,,The sound is too dull to be Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:35.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! He played a stone on something we're selling!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You worthless brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:42.13,Background,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. A little child played a\Nstone on a board we're selling, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to make you pay for the Go\Nboard you scratched if you say anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:04.67,Background,,0,0,0,,U-Umm... I think I'll wait until I\Nget a little better before I buy a board.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Go boards are made of wood, so it's\Ngoing to get dented if you play a stone on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really valuable, so please don't do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.66,Sai,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:23.57,Background,,0,0,0,,A Go board that Honinbou Shuusaku used?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're selling this, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,1,000... 10,000... 6,000,000!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a treasure that we got from\Nan antique shop just the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.98,0:07:41.66,Background,,0,0,0,,Master Shuusaku used this board\Nwhen he went to Takamatsu to tutor Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to Takamatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:47.39,Sai,,0,0,0,,I went to all sorts of places with Torajirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:53.27,Background,,0,0,0,,This is something that got stored\Nthere after Master Shuusaku signed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.05,Background,,0,0,0,,Gokiso the pro!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:59.54,Sai,,0,0,0,,Signed? In Takamatsu? Torajirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.96,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur2\fs35\t(1065,1440,1,\fs66.5)\1c&H09202F&\bord0\shad0\move(190,161,133,89,1065,1440)\b1}Honinbou Shuusaku{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.80,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\blur2\fs66.5\t(0,646,1,\fscx107\fscy107)\1c&H09202F&\bord0\shad0\move(133,89,125,78,0,646)\b1}Honinbou Shuusaku{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.99,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru! That's not Torajirou's writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:07.71,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fake!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You again!? It's the real thing! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:21.35,Sai,,0,0,0,,How dare you lie like that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not Shuusaku's writing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the real thing. There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,See! Even a pro says so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is a pro saying such a lie!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:37.08,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh! You must be the one\Nthat wrote this on the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How dare you say that to Mr. Gokiso!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the problem this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:48.23,Sai,,0,0,0,,How dare you slander\NTorajirou's name with a fake signature!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare... umm... what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.62,0:08:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:09:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gokiso, your tutoring game is\Nabout to start, please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Like anyone's going to pay\Nattention to what a kid says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:18.83,ed64_romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\blur1\1c&H052431&\bord0\frz283\move(236,222,125,222)\b1}Honinbou Shuusaku{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:13.80,Background,,0,0,0,,Fake... you can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:16.24,Background,,0,0,0,,Yup. They're both lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:18.62,Background,,0,0,0,,Those other boards aren't Kaya either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that might be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not Kaya, that's new Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know too much about it either,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but the vendor who came until\Nlast year was a very nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He taught me a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:43.59,Background,,0,0,0,,New Kaya is similar to Kaya, but its real\Nname is Spruce, and it's a foreign species of wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:47.44,Background,,0,0,0,,The board surface is smooth, so it's\Na great material for making boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:49.93,Background,,0,0,0,,But Kaya is more expensive than new Kaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:55.40,Background,,0,0,0,,so I hear that some immoral vendors\Nsell Spruce under the pretense of Kaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:56.62,Background,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you change vendors?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gokiso... the pro you\Nmet earlier, recommended him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Events like this can't be held\Nwithout the help of the pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep an eye on that vendor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well. We came all this way to enjoy\Nourselves. and this happens. Doesn't it suck, Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go watch another game?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's angry. He's angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:35.02,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:43.33,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs14.5\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz359\pos(288.,154)}Tutor Go Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.77,Sai,,0,0,0,,The man from earlier is playing a tutoring game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:42.95,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's playing the person who\Nran away without buying the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, look. You're falling apart everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The upper-left's died too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you just can't improve\Nwithout playing on a good board.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.88,0:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What a horrible game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:02.90,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes. The stronger player is\Njust picking on the weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.23,Sai,,0,0,0,,This is not a tutoring game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I can't do any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.19,0:11:10.61,Sai,,0,0,0,,You still have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have a chance, mister. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do at this point?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine with me, would you like to continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough. No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The child behind you says you can come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you play?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You did say all that, why don't you play?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:38.81,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:42.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Do you realize that he's a pro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.89,Sai,,0,0,0,,I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:48.45,Sai,,0,0,0,,Tell him to take Torajirou's\Nboard off the display if you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:49.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're really going to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If I win this game, take\NShuusaku's board off the display.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it your best shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:04.29,Background,,0,0,0,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:08.52,Thinking,,0,0,0,,But won't he raise a fuss later if I let Sai play?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:12.16,Sai,,0,0,0,,He thinks you're just a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:16.83,Sai,,0,0,0,,If he is to lose to you, he'll be\Ntoo ashamed to tell anyone about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.72,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.03,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Go, Sai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:22.72,Sai,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:26.20,Sai,,0,0,0,,14-4 approach by one space!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kurata, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.42,0:12:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I guess this is a\Ngood place to end the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kurata, may I have your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you get a title this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd like a title.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Meijin might be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well write it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.43,0:12:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Meijin, most of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:12:59.09,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz286\pos(233,470)}Atsushi
