Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:12:59.26,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs17.5\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz241\pos(528,384)}Most of the way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:12:59.38,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs17.5\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz241\pos(528,355)}Most of the way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.38,0:13:03.76,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs17.5\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz241\pos(528,345)}Most of the way
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.76,Background,,0,0,0,,Can't show this to Touya Meijin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, may I have an autograph, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do Kisei for this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon to be Kisei, Kurata Atsushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll take one with Honinbou, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually Honinbou, Kurata Atsushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds nice. I wouldn't be\Nsurprised if it really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.12,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scheduled for a tutoring game\Nwith you after this. Take it easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:34.79,Background,,0,0,0,,I should have taken Mr. Kurata, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.13,0:13:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had a tutoring game with Mr. Gokiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And what did Mr. Gokiso do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Horrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:49.62,Background,,0,0,0,,All his moves seemed to be\Ntraps, and he just pummeled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:54.04,Background,,0,0,0,,That's horrible. I wonder if\Nsomething bad had happened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:14:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I hear, Mr. Gokiso's stocks\Nwent down and he's in a bit of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He shouldn't be taking his anger\Nout us over something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I resigned quickly, and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Though the child behind me\Nsaid I could still make a come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to make a come\Nback against a pro after you fall behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If he could do that, it would\Nmean that he's stronger than a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:29.32,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.19,0:14:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The tutoring game from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That child continued\Nplaying, and it's turned around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:44.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It's over. This is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:46.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:50.33,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He plays moves that I would never have imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How... how can it be... it's got to be\Nbecause I underestimated him. It has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:57.79,Background,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:14:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurata-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I played an embarrassing game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd laugh over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It was funny? I\Nwould've liked to have seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.39,0:15:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:21.77,Sai,,0,0,0,,The promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't forget about your promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:24.95,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.32,Background,,0,0,0,,Did you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:31.95,Thinking,,0,0,0,,It was Sai who won, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I hear, you\Nmanaged to come back from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true? It can't be. Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a pro. If you could do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have I seen you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a pro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Shindou. I just became a pro this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I know! I saw you on Weekly Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I get it! You're a new first dan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.87,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, what was that promise you mentioned earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!... Oh! Mr. Kurata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, we don't have any goods worthy of you, today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya, 200,000. What's this price tag?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is... umm... ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:32.60,Background,,0,0,0,,I mean... this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I misplaced the tag! This is the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking the time to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, is there anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you sold a few already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Umm ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please show me a list of\Npeople who have bought from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:16:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A list?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.51,0:17:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I know nothing about Shuusaku's writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:11.30,Sai,,0,0,0,,A fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:14.01,Sai,,0,0,0,,For sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I said it's for sure, so it's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you said so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:21.25,Sai,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you do something about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take Shuusaku's board off display.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk to you in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you said so, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:44.50,Background,,0,0,0,,Just so that you know, don't be\Ntoo proud of beating Mr. Gokiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be incredible if you beat\Nme, but he's a pro who's over the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:53.99,Sai,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:18:03.73,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz4\pos(453,105)}Register
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.85,0:17:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? You don't know me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kurata! The pro player, Kurata!\NMost of the way Meijin or Honinbou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.57,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that strong, Mr. Kurata?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:09.03,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\frz4\pos(453,105)}Register
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But it's not that hard\Nto beat the people above you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone above me is desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya Meijin is at his peak right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man Kuwabara seems like he's got\Nit easy, but he's actually quite desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just barely protecting the title of\NHoninbou by using bluffs and mental traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll fall down soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,By either myself, or maybe\NOgata-san'll do it before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The really scary people are coming from below me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:50.32,Background,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm more scared of\NTouya Akira than Touya Kouyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:54.15,Background,,0,0,0,,The fights against the\Npeople below me will be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:19:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it's far in the future.\NFirst I have to bring down the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.96,Sai,,0,0,0,,He's really confident, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.02,0:19:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Shindou, Shindou Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not many people don't know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:16.13,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\fscy80\pos(288,56)}Register
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:14.67,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I have that fan?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.39,0:19:20.10,Background,,0,0,0,,You want it right, here you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:18.26,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\frz316\pos(647,485)}Kurata Atsushi
