Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.10,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\frz316\pos(447,372)}Kurata Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, that's store merchandise, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,umm... could you pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want it? You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding. But\Neveryone wants it. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a pro already, so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:42.79,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22.5\1c&H000000&\bord0\blur0.8\shad0\frz316\pos(84,348)}Shindou Hikaru
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:42.79,NoteArial,,0,0,0,,{\fs22.5\1c&H000000&\3c&HB5B2B5&\bord2\blur0.8\shad0\frz266\pos(356,270)}Kurata Atsushi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.04,0:19:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! You ruined my autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Idiot! Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you write such\Nugly letters next to my name!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,K-Kurata-san, your writing is just as bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:58.05,Sai,,0,0,0,,It really is poorly written,\NTorajirou's was so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're peculiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.27,0:20:06.48,Thinking,,0,0,0,,So are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! My tutoring games are about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll remember your name. As\NHoninbou Shuusaku's Writing Authenticator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:20.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Writing Authenticator?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret turning my autograph down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai, are you satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:35.26,Sai,,0,0,0,,Satisfied! Satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows a lot about Shuusaku's writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What a strange child.
