Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is called Kifu. If you place stones on the board
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.97,0:22:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,following these numbers,\Nyou can replay an old game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to give it a try?
