Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:43.09,NoteArial_Igo,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\q2\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(0,0)\fscx99\3c&H600037&\4c&H600037&\fscy90\bord1\shad0.5\move(1220,342,-560,342)}If you replay a Kifu, you can learn all sorts of things, like the flow of a game, attacking, and defending.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a match from hundreds of years\Nago can be replayed with just one Kifu.
