Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:23:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My first opponent is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:06.58,Sai,,0,0,0,,He's already declared hostilities against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.79,0:23:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shindou-kun's opponent for the first round is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up to Akira... I'll surpass him!
